OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying warm
OL,6,Fand at times muggy, whilst also
OL,7,Fremaining rather cloudy and damp, with
OL,8,Fspells of rain and drizzle at times,
OL,9,Fbut perhaps seen more widely towards
OL,10,Fdawn. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FRather cloudy with a little
OL,13,Frain possible during the morning
OL,14,Fespecially, but tending to become
OL,15,Fdrier into the afternoon, with some
OL,16,Fbright or sunny spells developing.
OL,17,FWarm, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
