OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMostly fine with some sunshine.
OL,7,FTurning very warm and humid towards
OL,8,Fthe weekend, staying mainly dry, but
OL,9,Fwith a small chance of thunderstorms
OL,10,Fon Friday and Saturday.
